TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {6609=Everything works smoothly and I never had the feeling that either of my tools were on their deathbeds, but since I'm starting to use them more after a semi-hiatus, they're starting to feel "tight". I'm particularly annoyed at the ISO 1600 limit on the camera, especially when doing macro. The slow continuous drive is also a bit of an annoyance in that area. The fact that the images are only 8 megapixels is starting to show at all times, though.}
